title: 2manydjs Takeover for Rob da Bank 02/02/2009
description:
Midnight - 2am 2manydjs in for Rob da Bank

2manydjs sit in for Rob da Bank and take over Radio 1's leftfield music show.

2manydjs aka David and Stephen Dewaele from Soulwax sit in for da Bank  with two exclusive and very special mixes, not to be missed.

Broadcast:    02 Feb 2009      00:00      BBC Radio 1, SAT.
